{"tid":257009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黑幫搵唔到食】淪落到超市偷米偷西瓜 成員：組織缺錢","createTime":"2017-05-25T02:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T05:34:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a85483b137079396179fe6f3292c503effd5a3b","tid":257009,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170524/large/1495597327_2e2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170524%2Flarge%2F1495597327_2e2b.jpg&h=631c7afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170525&amp;guid=56734434&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170525%26guid%3D56734434%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=1hWmPSacJKZtYHxjwETg5aS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=e5290e39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170525%26guid%3D56734434%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=ffd264c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170525&amp;guid=56734434&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n即時國際  2017-05-25 00:03:04 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n(互聯網)<br />\n日本愛知縣名古屋市三名山口組系的成員，因為在超市盜竊食品及日用品等被捕，他們直言因組織資金資乏，「為組織繼續生存」而犯案。<br />\n<br />\n事發在上月23日，當地時間下午7時20分左右，55歲組長郡司真人，帶同59歲幹部中島良輔以及52歲的飯田廣，齊齊到一間商場的超市盜竊。三人偷走西瓜、鰻魚、米共198件，總值76,120日圓（約5,300港元）的食品及日用品。郡司同日被捕，縣警周二發表中島及飯田被捕的消息。<br />\n<br />\n同為無業的中島及飯田承認犯案，中島直言：「組的營運資金緊絀，為了令組繼續生存下去，金錢是必要的。」<br />\n<br />\n日本山口組在戰後混亂時間，曾有過「輝煌歲月」，當年是收入高達數十億美元的犯罪組織，涉獵色情、賭業及毒品交易。與中國的三合會組織或意大利黑手黨不同，他們並不違法，一直受警方監管，曾被視為「維繫地方街頭秩序的必要邪惡勢力」。<br />\n<br />\n但近年經濟疲弱、社會容忍度降低及成員人數減少的情況下，當地黑幫越來越難生存。政府收緊反黑幫條例，令黑幫成員連開銀行戶口都難。這些因素被指是山口組高調分裂的原因之一。<br />\n<br />\n日本朝日新聞/法新社"},{"pid":"abdca9c0bbc33905443e63150d24ae19b9b604d7","tid":257009,"uid":49344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T02:19:00.000Z","msg":"成兩百件野點偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ffc0e34adcf3c730e8d1c9a2f1801c158e972d","tid":257009,"uid":82238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T02:34:51.000Z","msg":"點撚樣偷西瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb067d77edf21f8f4a742fb975d1de4389a815de","tid":257009,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T02:54:37.000Z","msg":"人總需要勇敢生存<br />\n我還是重新許願<br />\n例如學會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去偷西瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a07e7540bd94fac0dfaab7fed1398b364f4e1d","tid":257009,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T02:58:07.000Z","msg":"早排比人扣起左成億金條個走私賊有冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f1827836f7d7cbb8cfee1a66e955bbf43d9198","tid":257009,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T03:00:27.000Z","msg":"如果擺條囡係度 班人會唔會除左底褲"},{"pid":"d3d8cad8b106dea88e0d5c4b66857de1d527040b","tid":257009,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"山口組（廢中）"},{"pid":"56c70e85f3a13eeddb9a48724c27cf236b677f42","tid":257009,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"咁笨柒偷西瓜<br />\n又大又重又唔係貴"},{"pid":"abfb3fc56bbc7ea9844e3ae17d1f8d88d35ff89e","tid":257009,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T03:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山口組（廢中）</blockquote><br />\n係咪山口百惠歌迷群組咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a432d02b206b1ec7ffd3dcff3256b5375556b8","tid":257009,"uid":32836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,